SSH for terminal 1, 2 and 3:

ssh ubuntu@<TURTLEBOT_IP>
#ip address may vary
password: <PASSWORD>



Run this on Terminal 1 (Bringup):

export TURTLEBOT3_MODEL=waffle_pi
export LDS_MODEL=LDS-01
export ROS_DOMAIN_ID=27
source /opt/ros/humble/setup.bash
ros2 launch turtlebot3_bringup robot.launch.py



Run this on Terminal 2 (Activate Gas Sensor):

source /opt/ros/humble/setup.bash
export ROS_DOMAIN_ID=27
cd ~/ros2_ws
source install/setup.bash
ros2 run senseair_s8_driver senseair_s8_node



Run this on Terminal 3 (Image Publisher):

source /opt/ros/humble/setup.bash
export ROS_DOMAIN_ID=27
python3 image_publisher.py



Run this on Terminal 4 (Image Subscriber):

conda activate c1thesis
export PYTHONPATH="$CONDA_PREFIX/lib/python3.10/site-packages:$PYTHONPATH"
cd Documents/gas-leak-detection/SO34
export ROS_DOMAIN_ID=27
source install/setup.bash
ros2 run MEx3 gazzard_gui_detection_final

